<HTML><HEAD>    <TITLE></TITLE></HEAD><BODY BACKGROUND="blumarbl.gif"><FORM ENCTYPE="x-www-form-encoded" METHOD="POST" ACTION="default.cgi"><H1>Welcome to the NADE <IMG SRC="NADESPINanm.gif" WIDTH="119" HEIGHT="120"ALIGN="BOTTOM" NATURALSIZEFLAG="3"><BR>Technology SPIN homepage<BR><HR></H1><H2><CENTER>Preview</CENTER></H2><DL>  <DT>This web page provides a description of the <A HREF="#anchor21099">charter</A>of the National Association of Developmental Educators (NADE) TechnologySpecial Interest (SPIN) group, a <A HREF="Membership">l</A><A HREF="On-line.Experts">istingof the members</A> for the 1996/1997 year, and a listing of useful sitesfor developmental educators and students. Included in this membership listingis an e-mail link to an <A HREF="On-line.Experts">expert </A>who has identifiedhimself/herself as being willing to answer hardware (Mac or PC) and/or software(when using the computer as a tutor, the computer as a tool, or the computeras a tutee). The useful sites web page is in development and has been brokendown into professional organizations, professional resources, and studentresources. Finally, there is a form to fill out if you would like additionalinformation regarding membership in the <A HREF="#anchor134786">NADE TechnologySPIN.</A> </DL><H3><HR></H3><H2><CENTER><A NAME="anchor21099"></A>Charter<BR>of the<BR>NADE Technology SPIN</CENTER></H2><DL>  <DT>The NADE Technology SPIN (National Association of Developmental EducationSpecial Interest Group on Technology) was formed in 1995 to bring togethercollege level educators focused on using technology to develop studentsability to read, write, compute, and learn. This web page is an opportunityto document what we have done and to share our expertise with you. Feelfree to comment on these pages and inform us of links we could add. </DL><H5><A HREF="#anchor42281"><IMG SRC="return.back.button.GIF" WIDTH="27"HEIGHT="27" ALIGN="BOTTOM" NATURALSIZEFLAG="0">return to top of page</A></H5><H4><BR><HR></H4><H2><CENTER><A NAME="anchor134786"></A>Subscription to<BR>NADE Technology SPIN<BR><BR><FORM METHOD="POST" ACTION="fmpro.acgi$ADD"><pre><INPUT NAME="name" TYPE="reset" VALUE="Reset"></CENTER></H2><H4>Name <INPUT NAME="name" TYPE="text" SIZE="30" MAXLENGTH=80><BR><BR>Institution <INPUT NAME="name" TYPE="text" SIZE="59" MAXLENGTH=80><BR><BR>e-mail address <INPUT NAME="name" TYPE="text" SIZE="53" MAXLENGTH=80><BR></pre><INPUT value="Add" TYPE=submit>  <INPUT value="Start Over" TYPE=reset ></FORM><H5><A HREF="#anchor42281"><IMG SRC="return.back.button.GIF" WIDTH="19"HEIGHT="19" ALIGN="BOTTOM" NATURALSIZEFLAG="0">return to top of page</A></H5><P><CENTER><HR></CENTER><H3><CENTER></CENTER></H3><H2><CENTER>Send comments to Webmaster: <BR><A HREF="mailto:DC02@SWT.edu"><IMG SRC="mail.gif" WIDTH="40" HEIGHT="40"ALIGN="BOTTOM" NATURALSIZEFLAG="3"></A></CENTER></H2><ADDRESS><CENTER><B>Webmaster: David C. Caverly, Ph.D.; <BR>DC&Oslash;2@SWT.edu <BR>August, 1996</B></CENTER></ADDRESS></FORM></BODY></HTML>
