<HTML><HEAD>    <TITLE></TITLE></HEAD><BODY BACKGROUND="Ed.Tech.images/bkgrd.GIF" BGCOLOR="#ffffff"><P><CENTER><IMG SRC="Ed.Tech.images/image8.gif" WIDTH="497" HEIGHT="106"ALIGN=bottom NATURALSIZEFLAG="3"><BR><BR><A HREF="ed.tech.html">Ed. Tech Home</A> | <A HREF="about.lab.html">About thelab</A> | <A HREF="lab.hours.html">Lab hours</A> | <A HREF="lab.software.html">Software</A>| <A HREF="equipment.html">Equipment</A></CENTER><H2><HR WIDTH="97%" SIZE="4"><TT>About the lab...</TT></H2><DL><DD>The Educational Technology lab is located in room 4008 on the fourthfloor of the Education Building. The lab was established to support thetechnology lab component of CI4332 and CI3322. The lab is also used by severalgraduate classes as well as education students in general. </DL><H2><HR><TT>Who may use the lab?</TT></H2><DL><DD>The lab may be used by anyone who is currently taking a class in theC&amp;I deptartment<TT>.</TT>The lab may only be used during open hours.Open hours are times when a lab assistant is available and there are noscheduled labs. (<A HREF="lab.hours.html">seeLab Hours</A>). As there are many scheduled labs going on during the week,open times are limited. During open times students with assignments in CI3322 and CI4332 have priority over the equipment. </DL><BR><P>If you have any further questions please click on <!-- MailTo Tag --><A HREF="MAILTO:db15">Ed. Tech. Webmaster</A> or send e-mail to DB15. Answers to some of your questions will be included in <FONT SIZE=3>About the Lab</FONT> in the future.<HR></P><BR><P><CENTER><A HREF="ed.tech.html">Ed. Tech Home</A> | <A HREF="about.lab.html">About thelab</A> | <A HREF="lab.hours.html">Lab hours</A> | <A HREF="lab.software.html">Software</A>| <A HREF="equipment.html">Equipment</A></CENTER></BODY></HTML>
