<HTML><HEAD>    <TITLE></TITLE></HEAD><BODY BGCOLOR="#fff0bf" TEXT="#9e1211"><P><CENTER><A HREF="Mainpage.html"><IMG SRC="Graphics/image3.gif" WIDTH="32" HEIGHT="36" NATURALSIZEFLAG="0" ALIGN=middle BORDER="0">Main page</A>| <A HREF="Background.html">Background</A> | <A HREF="Criteria.html">Criteria</A>| <A HREF="Information.html">Information</A> | <A HREF="Nominations.html">Nominations</A>| <A HREF="Winner.html">Winner </A>| <A HREF="http://www.swt.edu/">SWTpage</A> </CENTER><H1><CENTER><IMG SRC="Graphics/image25.gif" WIDTH="468" HEIGHT="124" NATURALSIZEFLAG="0" ALIGN=bottom></CENTER></H1>This award will be given annually to the author/illustrator of the mostdistinguished book for children and young adults that authentically reflectsthe lives and experiences of Mexican Americans in the Southwestern regionof the United States.<BR><BR>In addition:<BR><BR>a) The author should be a U.S. citizen.<BR><BR>b) The portrayal/representations of Mexican Americans should be<BR>accurate and engaging, avoid stereotypes, and reflect rich<BR>characterization.<BR><BR>c) The book winning the award for a particular year must have been<BR>published for the first time within that calendar year. <BR><BR>d) The book may be fiction or non- fiction.<BR><BR>e) Children's input will be solicited on the nominated books.<BR><BR>f) The text and illustrations should be of highest quality.<BR><BR>g) Selections will be made from books nominated. If no book nominated isconsidered to<BR>meet the listed criteria, no award will be presented.<BR><BR>h) A regional committee will narrow the list of nominated books. A nationalcommittee<BR>will select the final winner.<BR><BR>The book chosen as an award winner will receive a $3000 cash award. Theauthor/illustrator of the book will receive or share the cash award andwill also receive a certificate with the award seal.<BR>Ceremonies to acknowledge the award will take place on the Southwest TexasState University campus each fall during Hispanic Heritage Month.<BR><A HREF="Mainpage.html"><BR><BR><IMG SRC="Graphics/image3.gif" WIDTH="32" HEIGHT="36" NATURALSIZEFLAG="0"ALIGN=middle BORDER="0">Main page</A> | <A HREF="Background.html">Background</A>| <A HREF="Criteria.html">Criteria </A>| <A HREF="Information.html">Information</A>| <A HREF="Nominations.html">Nominations </A>| <A HREF="Winner.html">Winner</A>| <A HREF="http://www.swt.edu/">SWT page</A> </BODY></HTML>
