hrough portfolios, stasticallyevaluating that progress, document accumulated knowledge, construct anddocument knowledge through word processors, spreadsheets, and graphic programs</TD></TR> <TR> <TD><B>diagnostic</B></TD> <TD>Accuplacer<BR>E-LASSI<BR>GUIDES<BR>Informal Reading Placement Test<BR>Vocabulary Placement Test</TD> <TD>Grady Profile<BR>Informal Reading Placement Test</TD> </TR> <TR> <TD><B>management</B></TD><TD>Excel<BR>FileMaker Pro<BR>FoxPro<BR>Fry Readability Formula<BR>SPSS<BR>StatView<BR>Word<BR>Works</TD> <TD>Excel<BR>FileMaker Pro<BR>FoxPro<BR>Fry Readability Formula<BR>SPSS<BR>StatView<BR>Word<BR>Works </TD></TR> <TR><TD><B>production</B></TD> <TD>Canvas<BR>Crossword Magic<BR>Director<BR>Drill<BR>Drill Maker<BR>Exam Builder<BR>Impact<BR>LinxLite<BR>Linx Industrial<BR>MORE<BR>OmniPage<BR>PageMaker<BR>Persuasion<BR>PowerPoint<BR>PrintShop<BR>Word<BR>WordSearch<BR>WordPerfect</TD> <TD>Canvas<BR>Crossword Magic<BR>Director<BR>MORE<BR>OmniPage<BR>PageMaker<BR>Persuasion<BR>PowerPoint<BR>PrintShop<BR>Word<BR>WordSearch<BR>WordPerfect</TD> <TR><TD><B>utilities</B></TD> <TD>Access PC<BR>AfterDark<BR>Crash Barrier<BR>Double Density<BR>Mac-in-Dos<BR>Norton Utilities<BR>PC-Rx<BR>Run PC<BR>Soft Windows<BR>Stuffit Deluxe<BR>Symantec Antivirus<BR>Timbuktu Pro<BR>Virex</TD> <TD>Access PC<BR>AfterDark<BR>Crash Barrier<BR>Double Density<BR>Mac-in-Dos<BR>Norton Utilities<BR>PC-Rx Run PC<BR>Soft Windows<BR>Stuffit Deluxe<BR>Symantec Antivirus<BR>Timbuktu Pro <BR>Virex</TD></TR> <TR><TD> <H3>Computer as Tutor</H3></TD> </H3><TD>Computer is used to teach, provide practice, and reteacha sequence of skills</TD> <TD>Computer is used to document growing knowledgeand to simulate authentic learning tasks</TD> </TR> <TR> <TD><B>drill/practice</B></TD><TD>Algebra Drill and Practice I, II, III<BR>Algebra 1-6<BR>Calculus 1-6<BR>High Steps to Comprehension<BR>Intellectual Pursuits<BR>Practical Comprehension<BR>Practical Grammar I, II, III<BR>Spellit Plus<BR>Statsitics I, II<BR>STUDYMATE - The Grade Booster<BR>Word Attack</TD> <TD>SimpleText</TD> </TR> <TR> <TD><B>tutorial</B></TD><TD>Analogies<BR>Advanced Analogies<BR>College Bound Analogies<BR>Comprehension Connection<BR>Essential Grammar<BR>Essential Punctuation<BR>Figurative Language<BR>First Year Algebra<BR>Learning Plus<BR>Nuts and Hyperbolts<BR>Primary Steps to Comprehension<BR>Reading & Writing Connection<BR>Reading Realities At-Risk Series<BR>SEEN<BR>Steps to Comprehension<BR>Textbook Marking Strategies<BR>Tips for College Test Taking<BR>Urban Reader<BR>Using your Biology Textbook Effectively<BR>Using your Psychology Textbook Effectively</TD> <TD>Textbook Marking Strategies<BR>Tips for College Test Taking<BR>Using your Biology Textbook Effectively<BR>Using your Psychology Textbook Effectively</TD> </TR> <TR><TD> <B>simulation</B></TD> <TD>Collaborative Writer<BR>Research Paper Writer<BR>Where in the World, USA, Time, America's Past, Space is Carmen San Diego<BR>Writer's Helper<BR>Write This Way/LD</TD> <TD>Beethoven - CD-ROM<BR>Collaborative Writer<BR>EndNote Plus<BR>Hitchhiker's Guide to the Galaxy<BR>Idea Fisher<BR>Idea Liner<BR>Inside Information<BR>Inspiration<BR>Learning Tool<BR>Mindlink<BR>MORE<BR>Research Paper Writer<BR>Where in the World, USA, Time, America's Past, Space is Carmen San Diego<BR>Writer's Helper</TD> </TR> <TR><TD><H3>Computer as Tutee</H3></TD><TD>Computer is used by the instructor to develop professionally through telecommunications and to develop hypermedia drill/practice or tutorial courseware.</TD> <TD>Computer is used by both the instructor and students to develop; to explore reading/writing through telecommunications; to document their coming understanding of strategies through hypermedia</TD> </TR> <TR><TD> <B>telecommunications</B> </TD> <TD>KermitMailMicrophoneNetScape NavigatorProComm</TD> <TD>KermitMailMicrophoneNetScape NavigatorProComm</TD> </TR> <TR><TD><B>hypermedia</B> </TD> <TD>Authorware ProfessionalFourmatHypercardLesson WriterLinkwayPLUSQuestTextbook Toolbook</TD> <TD>HypercardLinkwayPLUSTextbook Toolbook</TD></TR> </TABLE> <P><CENTER><HR></CENTER><CENTER><A NAME="anchor269466"></A><H1>Software Reviews</H1></CENTER><P><H4>Soon this will be a place where you can leave a software review.</H4><P><CENTER><HR></CENTER><P><H1><A NAME="anchor23779"></A><CENTER>Publisher's Addresses</CENTER></H1><P><BR><P><I>Access PC</I><BR>Insignia <BR>526 Clyde Ave. <BR>Mountain View, CA 94043 <P><I>Accuplacer</I><BR>The College Board <BR>5 Columbus Ave.<BR>New York, NY 10023-6992<P><I>After Dark</I><BR>Berkeley Systems<BR>2095 Rose St.<BR>Berkeley, CA 94709<P><I>Algebra Drill and Practice I, II, III</I><BR>Conduit<BR>University of Iowa, Oakdale Campus<BR>Iowa City, IA 52242 <P><I>Algebra 1-6</I><BR>Professor Weissman Software<BR>P.O. Box 140612<BR>Staten Island, NY 10314<P><I>Analogies Advanced</I><BR>Hartley Software<BR>133 Bridge St.<BR>Dimondale, MI 48821<P><I>Analogies College Bound</I><BR>Hartley<BR>133 Bridge St.<BR>Diamondale, MI 48821<P><I>Analogies Tutorial</I><BR>Hartley<BR>133 Bridge St.<BR>Diamondale, MI 48821<P><I>Authorware Professional</I><BR>Authorware, Inc.<BR>275 Shoreline Drive, Suite 535 <BR>Redwood City, CA 94065<P><I>Beethoven - CD ROM</I><BR>Voyager<BR>1351 Pacific Coast Highway<BR>Santa Monica, CA 90401<P><I>Calculus 1-6</I><BR>Professor Weissman Software<BR>P.O. Box 140612<BR>Staten Island, NY 10314<P><I>Canvas</I><BR>Deneba Software<BR>7400 S.W. 87th. St.<BR>Miami, FL 33173<P><I>Collaborative Writer</I><BR>Research Design Associates<BR>10 Boulevard Ave<BR>Greenlawn, NY 11740<P><I>Comprehension Connection</I><BR>Milliken Publishing Co.<BR>1100 Research Blvd., <BR>P.O. Box 21579<BR>St. Louis, MO 63132<P><I>Crash Barrier</I><BR>Casady and Greene<BR>22734 Portola Dr.<BR>Salinas, CA 93908<P><I>Critical Thinking: