<HTML><HEAD>
<TITLE>MASALink</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<FRAMESET COLS="128,*" BORDER=0 FRAMEBORDER=0 FRAMESPACING=0>
<FRAME SRC="depart.htm" MARGINHEIGHT="0" NAME="TOC">
<FRAME SRC="masafram.htm" NAME="main">
</FRAMESET><NOFRAMES>
<BODY background="pics/PARCH.GIF">
<IMG align=LEFT SRC="pics/MASASEAL.GIF">
<P ALIGN=LEFT>

<BR><B><I><FONT SIZE=2>
<HR>
Since its organization in 1873, the Medical Association
of the State of Alabama has remained committed to maintaining the highest
standards of medical care for all Alabamians, a commitment demonstrated
over the years in unparalleled dedication to public health; in unflagging
support for the highest standards of medical education; and in devotion
to the ideals enunciated by Doctor Tinsley Harrison, that &quot;no greater
opportunity responsibility or obligation can fall to the lot of a human
being&quot; than to serve as a physician.</FONT></I></B>
<BR>
<HR>
<BR>
<CENTER><FONT SIZE=5><B>
<A NAME="MTOP">MASALink</A></B></FONT><BR>
<FONT SIZE=3><B>
A MEMBER SERVICE OF THE MEDICAL ASSOCIATION OF THE STATE OF ALABAMA
</B></FONT></CENTER>
<BR>

