<HEAD>

<TITLE>EXECUTIVE DIRECTOR SEARCH</TITLE>

<META NAME="GENERATOR" CONTENT="Internet Assistant for Microsoft Word 2.0z">
</HEAD>

<BODY BACKGROUND="../pics/PARCH.GIF">

<P><B>
<HR><P>
<CENTER><FONT SIZE=5 FACE="Times New Roman">EXECUTIVE DIRECTOR SEARCH
<P><HR></B>
<BR>
</FONT></CENTER>
<P>
<FONT FACE="Times New Roman" SIZE=4>
The Medical Association State of Alabama invites applications for the
position of Executive Director.  The current director has announced
that he plans to retire no later than December 31, 1997.
<BR><BR>
Applicants should have a college degree, excellent oral and written
communication skills, administrative and budgetary experience.
Previous experience with a medical association is ideal.
<BR><BR>
Send letter of introduction, resume, and names of at least three
references to:
<BR><BR>
<Center>
Search Committee<BR>
P.O. Box 2946<BR>
Tuscaloosa, AL  35403<BR><BR>
</CENTER>
</FONT>
