Contact:  1-800-847-7378  Ext. 400</B><BR>
<BR>

</TD></TR>

<TR><TD ALIGN="LEFT" VALIGN="TOP" WIDTH=313><B>Discount Magazine Subscriptions at low rates for use in your office <BR>
MASA Magazine <BR>
