<P>
<CENTER><B><FONT SIZE=6>Physician Placement Register<BR>
</FONT><FONT SIZE=4>The Medical Association of the State of Alabama</FONT></B></CENTER>
<HR>
<P>
<B>DECEMBER, 1996<BR>
<BR>
</B>The <B>Physician Placement Register </B>is published as a
service of the Medical Association of the State of Alabama to
provide physicians with information on where practice opportunities
are available. Information on physicians who wish to locate in
Alabama is also provided.<BR>
<BR>
The <B>Register</B> is published quarterly through the Department
of Public Relations of the Medical Association. For questions
or comments, please call <B>Victor R. McLean, Director of Public
Relations</B>, at 334-263-6441.<BR>
<BR>
For information or to submit a listing for the publication, please
contact:<BR>
<BR>
<P ALIGN="CENTER">
<CENTER><B>Billie H. Hicks, Editor<BR>
Physician Placement Register<BR>
P.O. Box 1900<BR>
Montgomery, Alabama 36102-1900<BR>
Telephone: 334-263-6441<BR>
</P><BR>
</B></CENTER>
<P ALIGN="LEFT">
Although the Medical Association of the State of Alabama believes
the Physician Placement Register notices on the following pages
to be from reliable sources, the Association does not investigate
the organizations or individuals included and assumes no responsibility
concerning them. Every effort is made to avoid errors and/or omissions,
but the Association cannot accept responsibility for clerical
or printer's errors. (*indicates new listings.)<BR>
<BR>
<I><B>The deadline for submitting listings for the March, 1997
Register is February 15, 1997.<BR>
</B></I>
<HR>
