<DOCOLDNO>IA068-000423-B023-251</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www.masalink.org:80/yps/YPSFIN.HTM 199.44.130.210 19970113073042 text/html 7017
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.1
Date: Monday, 13-Jan-97 07:30:44 GMT
