<HTML>

</HEAD>
<TITLE>Library and Documentation</TITLE>
<HEAD>

<BODY BACKGROUND="spiral.jpg">

<B><H2>Library and Documentation</H2>
<P>
The Academy has a small specialised library, whose books and documents
may be consulted during opening hours. Students also have access
to the main University Library, the Library of the International
Maritime Law Institute, and to public specialised libraries elsewhere.
<P>
The Academy has established a computerised databank containing
a considerable number of important documents and also has access
to remote databases via Internet. In the course
of the academic year, it is expected that the Academy will greatly
extend its own databanks and improve its access to sources abroad.
<P>
</B>
<HR>
</BODY>
</HTML>

