<HR>

<H3>Welcome to MedGate</H3>

<P>
<STRONG>MedGate</STRONG> is a joint initiative by the <A HREF="nshome.htm" >North-South Centre</A>  
<!--jump to nscentre homepage -->
of the Council of Europe, the <!--jump to homepage of academy -->

<A HREF="mads/www.htm" >Mediterranean Academy of Diplomatic Studies</A>  
in Malta and the <A HREF="link.htm" >Centre d'Informaci i Documentaci Internacionales a Barcelona</A>,
<!-- jump to cidob homepage-->
which aims to help keeping you informed about what is going
on in the Mediterranean.
<P>
<STRONG>MedGate</STRONG> will help you find continously updated
information about social, economic, political, cultural and accademic
events taking place in the Mediterranean, as well as link you
to the homepages of the different organisations working on this
issues in the Mediteranean.
<P>
<CENTER> 
<IMG ALIGN=MIDDLE SRC="mapa1.gif" ALT="Old map of Mediterranean" >
</CENTER> 
<P>
<STRONG>MedGate</STRONG> has been structured to help you find
the information you need in the fastest posible way. Please click
on one of the following items to start your search:
<MENU>
<LI><A HREF="medcal.htm" >Calendar  </A>
<LI><A HREF="whoiswho.htm" >Who is Who?  </A>
<LI><A HREF="news.htm" >News and Facts  </A>
<LI><A HREF="map.htm" >Countries  </A>
<LI><A HREF="topics.htm" >Topics  </A>
<LI><A HREF="docs.htm" >Publications  </A>
<P>
<LI><A HREF="quiz.htm" >Do you know?  </A><BR>

</MENU>

<P>
<I><B>Disclaimer</B>: Medgate provides you with links to information
and Web-pages of a wide array of organisations. The North-South
Centre, nor any of the other initiative partners guarantee the
correctness of the information provided nor the quality of the
individual home pages MedGate can connect you with. Any information
given reflects the opinion of the providing organisation alone
and not necessarily that of the North-South Centre, the initiative
partners or any other organisation participating in the MedGate
project.</I>
<P>
<I>Please contact the North-South Centre on the address given
below if you find any information on MedGate that is incorrect
or outdated. Thank you.</I><HR>

<ADDRESS>
<CENTER>  For more information about Medgate please contact the
North-South Centre, Tel (351-1) 352 4954, E-mail: nscentre@telepac.pt</CENTER> 

