<H3>Welcome to MedGate</H3>
<STRONG>MedGate</STRONG> is a joint  initiative by the<A HREF="http://neon.coe.fr//NSCDATA/nshome.htm"> North-South Centre</A> of the Council of Europe, the <A HREF="http://www.unige.ch/mads">Mediterranean Academy of Diplomatic Studies</A> in Malta and the<A HREF=""> Centre d'Informaci i Documentaci Internacionales a Barcelona</A> , which aims to help keeping you informed about what is going on in the Mediterranean.<P>   

<STRONG>MedGate</STRONG> will help you find continously updated information about social, economic, political, cultural and accademic events taking place in the Mediterranean, as well as link you to the homepages of the different organisations working on this issues in the Mediteranean.<P>

<STRONG>MedGate</STRONG> has been structured to help you find the information you need in the fastest posible way. Please click on one of the following items to start your search:<P>

<MENU>
<LI><A HREF="medcal.htm">Calendar</A>
<LI><A HREF="whoiswho.htm">Who is Who?</A>
<LI><A HREF="news.htm">News and Facts</A>
<LI><A HREF="map.htm">Countries</A>
<LI><A HREF="topics.htm">Topics</A>
<LI><A HREF="tmplate3.htm">Publications</A>
</MENU>
<BR>


<I><B>Disclaimer</B>: Medgate provides you with links to information and Web-pages of a wide array of organisations. The North-South Centre, nor any of the other initiative partners guarantee the correctness of the information provided nor the quality of the individual home pages MedGate can connect you with. Any information given reflects the opinion of the providing organisation alone and not necessarily that of the North-South Centre, the initiative partners or any other organisation participating in the MedGate project.<P>

Please contact the North-South Centre on the address mentioned below if you find any information on MedGate that is incorrect or outdated. Thanks.<P>
</I>
<HR WIDTH=80% ALIGN=center><P>
