<P>
<B><FONT SIZE=4>INTRODUCTION TO THE LAW OF TREATIES<BR>
</FONT></B><I><FONT SIZE=2>by Professor Dietrich Kappeler</FONT></I>
<HR>

<P>
Distance-learning Course &quot;Introduction to the Law of Treaties&quot;
consists of the following modules:<BR>

<P>
First module<BR>

