<HEAD>
<TITLE>Who is Who in the Mediterranean</TITLE>
<!--Author: Bas Klein, The North-South Centre
Date: 6 September 1995
Project: Medgate-->
</HEAD>

<BODY>
<CENTER><H1>WHO IS WHO</H1></CENTER>
<CENTER><H1>In the Mediterranean</H1></CENTER>

<HR WIDTH=80% ALIGN=center>
<BR>
This page provides you with a list of international organisations dealing with Mediterranean issues as well as a list of experts/personalities active in the region. Please click on one of the country names if you are interested in a list of national organisations in that particular country.<P>

<HR WIDTH=80% ALIGN=center>

<CENTER><H3>International Organisations</H3></CENTER>

<MENU>
<LI><A HREF="nshome.htm">North-South Centre</A> of the Council of Europe
<LI><A HREF="link.htm">Euro-Arab Youth Dialogue</A>
<LI><A HREF="link.htm">European Youth Centre</A>
<LI><A HREF="link.htm">Youth Forum of the European Union</A>
<LI><A HREF="link.htm">Etc</A>.
</MENU>

<HR WIDTH=80% ALIGN=center>

<CENTER><H3>Experts and Personalities</H3></CENTER>
<MENU>
<LI><A HREF="link.htm">Mr. Jos Lemmers</A>, Executive Director of the North-South Centre.
<LI><A HREF="link.htm">Fifi Benaboud</A> Mediterranean Expert
<LI><A HREF="link.htm">Etc</A>.
</MENU>

<HR WIDTH=80% ALIGN=center>

<CENTER><H3>National Organisations</H3></CENTER>

<CENTER>Please click on one of the country names, organisations working on Mediterranean issues in countries outside of the Mediterranean basin are mentioned under other countries.</CENTER>


<CENTER><TABLE CELLSPACING=30%>
<TH><A HREF="country.htm#org">Albania</A><BR>
<A HREF="country.htm#org">Algeria</A><BR>
<A HREF="country.htm#org">Bosnia</A><BR>
<A HREF="country.htm#org">Cyprus</A><BR>
<A HREF="country.htm#org">Croatia</A><BR>
<A HREF="country.htm#org">Egypt</A><BR>
