<CENTER><H2>Resources Template </H2></CENTER>

This is a template for a WEB-page with information on resources on Mediterranean issues. Please load this template in the HTML editor and fill in the information below. Please take care not to delete any of the HTML markers. e-mail this page to the North-South Centre or send it on diskette to the address below.<P>

<CENTER><H2>Type here the name of the resource</H2></CENTER>

<B>Type of resource:</B> type here the type of resource (report, publication, newsletter, education pack, video etc).<P>

<H3>Description:</H3>

Please give a short description here of the resource. In the case of publications this should include a short summary, writers/editors and ISBN number.  In that case please separate the summary from the description text with a paragraph marker (see the help file of your HTML Editor).

<H3>Available from:</H3>

Organisation (if applicable)<BR>
Function (if applicable)<BR>
